message: Citation needed for this. There is ZERO evidence to support such a baseless assumption. Don't revert this, otherwise Wikipedia is a hypocrite for supporting unreliable (and thus uncredible) statements.
IT'S IMPOSSIBLE TO OVERLOAD THE MACHINES, YOU RETARDS!
Impossible to overload machine. Vibranium core prevents damage. Was never stated on-screen or off-screen.

They never overloaded the machine. The vibranum core would prevent damage to the anti-gravity machine, and thus it is logically impossible. What was shown explicitly on-screen however, was that Thor's strike destroyed the landmass. That's all.
